OrbitalFlights.Notes: Explosion in Service Module crippled spacecraft, resulting in mission abort. Mission aborted due to CSM malfunction. LM used to help bring crew back to Earth.

OrbitalFlights.Notes: Final circumlunar flight of the Zond program.
